"   typing '{' 3 times creates a fold marker in this vimrc.
"   close it with a comment after the mapping.
"   https://stackoverflow.com/a/24717020
nnoremap <space>/f :BLines {{{$<cr>| " }}}
nnoremap <space>/z :call <sid>SearchInFold()<cr>
